To stick a button to the left bottom corner of an ImGui window, you can use a combination of `ImGui::GetWindowDrawList()`, `ImGui::GetWindowPos()`, and `ImGui::GetWindowContentRegionMin()` functions to calculate the position of the bottom-left corner of the window. Here's an example:

